WEBVTT

00:00:00.913 --> 00:00:04.310
I'd like you to imagine
what it would feel like

00:00:04.334 --> 00:00:08.569
if, for two whole minutes,
your left arm was continuously flapping,

00:00:09.405 --> 00:00:11.947
your eyes were constantly rolling,

00:00:11.971 --> 00:00:13.901
your jaw was clenching so hard

00:00:13.925 --> 00:00:16.701
that it felt like your teeth
were about to break,

00:00:16.725 --> 00:00:18.432
and every ten seconds,

00:00:18.456 --> 00:00:22.734
you were forced to let out
a loud, high-pitched screech.

00:00:22.758 --> 00:00:24.202
(Tic)

00:00:25.149 --> 00:00:28.712
This is how I lived
at the young age of six,

00:00:28.736 --> 00:00:31.881
every waking moment, seven days a week.